          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span class="faq-q-text">Who writes the content brief?</span><span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span></button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Typically an editor, content strategist, or SEO specialist writes the brief. In smaller teams the writer briefs themselves using a template. AI tools like Frase, Clearscope, and MarketMuse can now auto-generate the SEO portion of a brief in minutes.</p></div></div>
