            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Target and secondary keywords, search intent, suggested title, H2/H3 outline, word count target, audience description, tone guidelines, internal linking targets, competitor URLs to reference, and clear success criteria.</p></div></div>
          </div>
