            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span class="faq-q-text">How long does it take to create a content brief?</span><span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span></button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>A standard blog brief typically takes 15-30 minutes to build. AI tools can cut that to 5-10 minutes for the SEO scaffolding. Enterprise-tier briefs with buyer-persona insights and audience research can take 60-90 minutes.</p></div></div>
